Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends},pocketsphinx,sphinxbase,libblas3,libasound2,libblas-dev,libasound2-dev,matrix-creator-malos,matrix-creator-init,libmatrix-malos-dev,protobuf
Description: Voice commands for MATRIX Creator hardware via ZMQ callback.
 Matrix Creator (https://creator.matrix.one) is a board that can be added
 to a Raspberry Pi v2 or v3. This board has many sensors and microphones. 
 This program allows other programs to access the board hardware via ZMQ and
 receive voice commands from its microphones.
